title: Independent 55+ 1 BR Apartment Living - Reserve Your New Home Today!
posting_body: ['Take a Video Tour Today', '> Check out the video walkthroughs of our community’s amenities and apartment homes!', 'If you are interested in an in-person tour, feel free to call or email us at any time.', 'Please use the link in this ad to view our video tours & options to contact us directly.', 'Updated and beautiful apartment home available in St Anthony MN for those 55 and better!', 'Legends at Silver Lake Village has all perks you could want, including a theater room, a 24-hour fitness center, a library, craft room, guest suite and more.', 'It’s a home perfect for hosting the grand-kids and other visiting family and friends.', 'Plus, our supreme location provides a wide range of nearby neighborhood bonuses, including Silver Lake Village Shops (anchored by Cub Foods), Silverwood Park, and Silver Lake.', 'What could be better?', 'Community Amenities Include:', '- On-Site Shuttle Bus Service', '- Pet Friendly Community', '- Near Salo Park with Outdoor Amphitheater & Free Concerts', '- Full-Size, Energy-Star Washer & Dryer', 'In EVERY Home!', '- Professional On-Site Management Team', '- Spacious Walk-In Closet(s)', '- Walk-In Bathroom Shower or Large Bathtub', 'We are a pet-friendly community.', 'Dogs & cats welcome!', '*Comfortable living does not have to be high dollar.', 'The Legends at Silver Lake Village is a 55 or better senior community and participates in an affordable housing program.', 'Household income & student status limitations apply: 1 Occupant: $49,320 | 2', 'Occupants: $56,340 | 3', 'Occupants: $63,360 | 4 Occupants: $70,380.', 'To maintain the integrity of the community; credit, rental & public record background checks are conducted on all applicants.', 'Office Hours:', 'Monday-Friday:9:00AM-5:00PM', 'Call today to learn more about our community:', 'show contact info', 'Legends at Silver Lake Village', '2500 38th Avenue Northeast', 'St. Anthony, MN, 55421', '<URL>', '*Some Restrictions May Apply.']
